        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The particles exert forces on each other that have the same magnitude. The charge of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Y</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is twice that of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>X</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, so the acceleration of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Y</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is half that of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>X</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The electric charge of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Y</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is twice that of particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>X</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, so particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Y</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> exerts an electric force on particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>X</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> that is twice as great as the electric force particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>X</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> exerts on particle <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Y</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>",
